            a(href='/my-works.html').button-form.button-form-left.authorization-author__left-but Мои работы
            a(href='/about.html').button-form.authorization-form__but-mid Обо мне
            a(href='/blog.html').button-form.button-form-right.authorization-author__right-but  Блог
